comments: Huerter (SAC) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Beverley (CHI) briefly places two hands on Fox (SAC) during the drive and marginal contact occurs before he removes them.
Sabonis' (SAC) pass is deflected out of bounds by LaVine (CHI).
Beverley (CHI) makes contact with the ball that dislodges it from Sabonis (SAC) during his upward shooting motion.
Beverley (CHI) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Vucevic (CHI) and Sabonis (SAC) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs during the inbound pass.
Sabonis' (SAC) shot attempt fails to make contact with the rim prior to the shot clock expiring.
Sabonis (SAC) initiates contact with DeRozan's (CHI) arm during the drive, that affects DeRozan's ability to gather the ball. A personal foul should have been assessed.
Vucevic (CHI) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Huerter (SAC) establishes himself in LaVine's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Barnes (SAC) initiates contact with LaVine's (CHI) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Beverley (CHI) initiates contact with Barnes' (SAC) arm on the perimeter.
Barnes (SAC) brings his arm toward LaVine (CHI) and marginal contact occurs during LaVine's (CHI) drive.
DeRozan (CHI) commits a take foul on Edwards (SAC).

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Barnes (SAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Barnes (SAC) makes contact with DeRozan's (CHI) elbow, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Dosunmu (CHI) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it away from LaVine (CHI).
